cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on accelerating the computation of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for computer vision tasks such as image classification and object detection. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a nonlinear optimization method, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of deep neural networks, which is a subfield of neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method on image datasets, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
